title: Mr Ed [talking horse] Ed The Songwriter 29 Mar 1961
description:
A horse is a horse of course, of course. But in the case of Mister Ed, he s much more! A stallion with the gift of the gab, Mister Ed burst out of the gate in 1961 and became one of the most beloved four-legged stars in TV history.The plain-speaking palamino and his hapless owner Wilbur have a timeless appeal that has earned the show fans around the world. So pull up a bale of hay and get ready to enjoy the wit and wisdom of Mister Ed.

Black and white. Mono. DVD rip. Avi. 25 mins

From The Best of Mister Ed. Volume 1. Disk 1A.
Title 2. First aired: 29 Mar, 1961.
Ed The Songwriter
